title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-28-2014 FRI
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-28-2014 FRI...PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program

The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 2/28/14Friday, February 28, 2014


Glenn went to the movies and he is not happy.
  He saw a big blockbuster this weekend that took aim
     at Libertarians and our troops,
       portraying them as terrorists 
         and he does not want you to see this movie,
             be warned, there are spoilers.
 
     Also, the new rise of anti-antisemitism and whom they identify with politically.

  Plus, the dangers of where the FCC is taking our freedom of the press,
      
      and Mike Rowe joins the program to discuss how the media is attacking him.
